WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:06.000
Daily exercise doesn't have to mean a gym.

00:06.000 --> 00:16.000
It can be a walk. A few stairs. Light stretching. Chair exercises. A swim. A slow lap around the block. The win is movement.

00:16.000 --> 00:26.000
Daily movement can help your body use insulin better, steady your blood sugar, improve circulation, help your heart, lower stress, and build strength.

00:26.000 --> 00:34.000
And strength matters. It's about staying mobile, protecting your feet, your balance, your confidence.

00:34.000 --> 00:44.000
So start small. Ten minutes counts. One walk counts. Doing it again tomorrow counts even more.

00:44.000 --> 00:51.000
The goal isn't perfection. It's a daily rhythm your body can trust.

00:51.000 --> 00:59.000
Diabetes is a 24/7 job. You don't have to carry it alone.

00:59.000 --> 01:06.000
LocalDiabetic. We just help you carry the day. Win big.
